,"settings":{"heading":"<b>Extra Storage Space<\/b>","text":"<p>Maximize your bedroom space with our divan bed featuring a divan base with drawers for seamless storage solutions. Our thoughtfully designed bed combines comfort with practicality, offering built-in drawers to effortlessly declutter your space. Experience the perfect blend of style and functionality as you tuck away blankets, linens, or personal items in our king size divan bed with storage.<\/p>","content_align":"text-start","hotspot_x":37,"hotspot_y":73}}},"block_order":["feature_LnhxWG","feature_8zgnca","feature_FhLJ9f"],"settings":{"product":"","show_content":true,"layout":"text_first","text_align":"text-center","mob_center_text":false,"heading_size":"h1","enlarge_text":false,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/sss_2_1.png","title":"Redefine Comfort With BedroomKing","description":"","button_label":"","button_link":"","hotspot_color":"#070707","color_scheme":"none","button_style":"btn btn--primary"}},"rich_text_Kpk3XR":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"subheading_3DwFy3":{"type":"subheading","settings":{"text":""}},"heading_tgig9x":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Key Features of BedroomKing's Divan Bed Frames","heading_size":"h3","heading_h1":false}}},"block_order":["subheading_3DwFy3","heading_tgig9x"],"settings":{"text_position":"justify-center","text_align":"text-center","mob_center_text":true,"color_scheme":"1","full_width":true,"prevent_animation":false}},"media_with_text_WrKJxt":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"heading_HaCXmN":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Easy to Assemble","heading_size":"h2","heading_h1":false}},"text_PUabAj":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Our divan bed frames are designed with simplicity in mind. Unlike traditional bed frames, divan beds are easy to assemble as it has one or two parts, making assembly easy and fast. We have easy-to-use <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/pages\/bed-assembly-instructions\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/pages\/bed-assembly-instructions\">assembly instructions<\/a> and hassle-free components, that can help you get your dream divan bed ready in no time. Enjoy the luxury of a stylish and comfortable sleep without any headache of hard assembly with our luxury king size and super king size divan bed frame. <\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_HaCXmN","text_PUabAj"],"custom_css":[".section__block.section__block--heading {font-size: 30px; color: #806642;}",".section__block.reading-width p {line-height: 1.8; font-size: 16px; color: #555;}"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Shopify_Mobile_portrait_7_1.png","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"left","image_fit":"contain","media_width":50,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none"}},"media_with_text_UetF78":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"heading_ryz3zp":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Free Headboard & Footboard","heading_size":"h2","heading_h1":false}},"text_UH9aRP":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Our Divan bed frame features a complimentary 26” headboard and a footboard. The headboard is built with high-quality materials that will last for years to come. Crafted with precision, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/ottoman-beds\/Divan-Drawer-Storage-Beds\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/ottoman-beds\/Divan-Drawer-Storage-Beds\">the divan bed frame with drawers<\/a> captures attention and makes your bedroom look sleek. Our divan bed frame is customisable with various fabrics and colour choices.  <\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_ryz3zp","text_UH9aRP"],"custom_css":[".cc-media-with-text {background: #efefef;}",".section__block.section__block--heading {font-size: 30px; color: #806642;}",".section__block.reading-width p {line-height: 1.8; font-size: 16px; color: #555;}"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Silver-Divan-bed.png","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"right","image_fit":"contain","media_width":50,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none"}},"slideshow_RMDWgN":{"type":"slideshow","blocks":{"slide_438RBF":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image_desktop":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Desktop_-_1_22.png","url":"","overlay_position":"justify-center items-center","overlay_text_align":"text-center","mob_center_text":false,"subheading":"","heading":"","heading_color":"#ffffff","heading_size":"h0","heading_h1":false,"text":"","enlarge_text":true,"button_1_label":"","button_1_link":"","button_1_style":"btn btn--primary","button_2_label":"","button_2_link":"","button_2_style":"btn btn--primary","transparent_content_color":"#ffffff","countdown_show":false,"countdown_end_date":"","countdown_end_time":"","countdown_end_text":"","enlarge_end_text":false,"countdown_hide_on_end":false,"use_custom_colors":false,"count_color":"#ffffff","bg_color":"#070707","bg_grad":""}}},"block_order":["slide_438RBF"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"height_mode":"auto","fixed_height_desktop":600,"fixed_height_mobile":350,"mobile_stacked":false,"nav_style":"slideshow_nav_lines","pagination_color":"#ffffff","nav_position":"justify-center","transition":"slide-fade","autoplay":true,"slider_pause":false,"autoplay_speed":5,"color_scheme":"white","full_width":true,"tint_color":"#000000","tint_opacity":0,"accessibility_info":"","prevent_animation":true}},"media_with_text_RMtjiR":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"heading_XdrNzz":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Divan Bed Size Options","heading_size":"h2","heading_h1":false}},"text_D4j7Rz":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Divan beds at Bedroomking are available in a lot of sizes from single to double divan beds. Choose from our range of bed<br\/>sizes – <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/3ft-single-beds\">3ft Single Beds<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/4ft-small-double\">4ft Small Double Beds<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/4ft6-double-beds\">4ft6 Double<br\/>Beds<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/5ft-king-size-beds\">5ft King Size Beds<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/6ft-super-king-size-beds\">6ft Super King Beds<\/a>.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_XdrNzz","text_D4j7Rz"],"custom_css":[".section__block.section__block--heading {font-size: 30px; color: #806642;}",".section__block.reading-width p {line-height: 1.8; font-size: 16px; color: #555;}"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DivanBedGrey_af50a7ed-b512-4d7b-8c22-c8b234f0d7b1.jpg","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"left","image_fit":"contain","media_width":50,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none"}},"media_with_text_p9Ln3N":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"heading_Pnh7hh":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Divan Bed Storage Options","heading_size":"h3","heading_h1":false}},"text_MGdp6Q":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Drawer divan beds offer practical under-bed storage solutions. Featuring smooth-gliding drawers, these beds provide ample space to store bedding, clothes, or other belongings. Ideal for maximising space in smaller bedrooms, drawer divan beds combine functionality with style. It comes with 2 drawers or 4 drawers under bed storage options. Explore our collection of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/divan-bed-sets\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.bedroomking.co.uk\/collections\/divan-bed-sets\">divan storage beds<\/a>.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_Pnh7hh","text_MGdp6Q"],"custom_css":[".cc-media-with-text {background: #efefef;}",".section__block.section__block--heading {font-size: 30px; color: #806642;}",".section__block.reading-width p {line-height: 1.8; font-size: 16px; color: #555;}"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Cube-Divan-Bed.png","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"right","image_fit":"contain","media_width":50,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none"}},"media_with_text_cBUcgr":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"heading_kttBV3":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"5 Years Warranty","heading_size":"h2","heading_h1":false}},"text_krxTXP":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Rest easy with our divan bed, backed by a robust 5-years warranty. Your satisfaction and peace of mind are our top priorities, and we stand by the quality of our products. Choose our divan bed – where style, comfort, and durability come together, and your satisfaction is guaranteed with our comprehensive 5-years warranty.<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_kttBV3","text_krxTXP"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/111_1708fa3b-013a-47c4-9028-119114eafef3.png","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"left","image_fit":"contain","media_width":50,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none"}},"slideshow_3e3jXr":{"type":"slideshow","blocks":{"slide_Fxpe39":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image_desktop":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/1800_X_900_8_10_c2baad8b-ea01-46b3-bcf3-b7acf9f2fe97.png","image_mobile":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/9_4df01413-a40d-485c-90db-b21f8918c4bf.png","url":"","overlay_position":"justify-center items-center","overlay_text_align":"text-center","mob_center_text":false,"subheading":"","heading":"","heading_color":"#ffffff","heading_size":"h0","heading_h1":false,"text":"","enlarge_text":true,"button_1_label":"","button_1_link":"","button_1_style":"btn btn--primary","button_2_label":"","button_2_link":"","button_2_style":"btn btn--primary","transparent_content_color":"#ffffff","countdown_show":false,"countdown_end_date":"","countdown_end_time":"","countdown_end_text":"","enlarge_end_text":false,"countdown_hide_on_end":false,"use_custom_colors":false,"count_color":"#ffffff","bg_color":"#070707","bg_grad":""}}},"block_order":["slide_Fxpe39"],"settings":{"height_mode":"auto","fixed_height_desktop":600,"fixed_height_mobile":350,"mobile_stacked":false,"nav_style":"slideshow_nav_lines","pagination_color":"#ffffff","nav_position":"justify-center","transition":"slide-fade","autoplay":true,"slider_pause":false,"autoplay_speed":5,"color_scheme":"white","full_width":true,"tint_color":"#000000","tint_opacity":0,"accessibility_info":"","prevent_animation":true}},"multi_column_kiEndT":{"type":"multi-column","blocks":{"column_Ed3rL4":{"type":"column","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/3_032256bf-7b0c-4190-86e8-f8c982451843.png","media_scale":100,"heading":"","text":"<p>Discover comfort and affordability with our divan bed, where a reasonable price meets exceptional quality. We believe in providing a luxurious sleep experience without breaking the bank. Our double divan bed with drawers offers the perfect balance of comfort, style, and value, ensuring you get the best night's sleep at a price that won't keep you up at night.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}},"column_nh3dgA":{"type":"column","settings":{"enable_media":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2_5b41f166-b61f-4c05-879b-12890deb3af4.png","media_scale":100,"heading":"","text":"<p>Now you can experience the luxurious texture and quality of our materials from the comfort of your home. Simply reach out to us, and we'll send you a complimentary fabric sample of our divan bed, allowing you to touch, see, and fall in love with the exceptional craftsmanship of our divan bed.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}}},"block_order":["column_Ed3rL4","column_nh3dgA"],"settings":{"title":"","heading_align":"text-start","button_label":"","button_link":"","layout":"grid","column_size":"medium","column_align":"center","image_ratio":"natural","color_scheme":"1","button_style":"btn btn--secondary"}},"testimonials_k78Di3":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"testimonial_twi4ep":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"testimonial":"<p>I feel like I'm sleeping on a cloud with this incredible divan bed! The comfort level is unmatched, and the strong divan base provides the perfect support for a restful night's sleep. The assembly was a breeze, and the bed's durability ensures I'll be enjoying my peaceful nights for years to come. A true game-changer!<\/p>","author":"SarahThompson","author_info":"","show_star_rating":true,"star_rating":5}},"testimonial_Pmtnra":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"testimonial":"<p>Not only is this divan bed a stylish addition to my bedroom, but the built-in storage drawers are a game-changer for keeping my space organized. The sleek design complements my room perfectly, and the quality is evident in every detail. A beautiful and functional choice for anyone looking to upgrade their sleep sanctuary!<\/p>","author":"Alex Martinez","author_info":"","show_star_rating":true,"star_rating":5}},"testimonial_DkmHBc":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"testimonial":"<p>I was pleasantly surprised by the affordability of this divan bed without compromising on quality. It's a dream come true for those on a budget! The<br\/>delivery was quick and hassle-free, and the bed's easy assembly was an added bonus. A fantastic find for anyone seeking a comfortable and cost-effective sleep solution<\/p>","author":"David Foster","author_info":"","show_star_rating":true,"star_rating":5}},"testimonial_XVbyqa":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"testimonial":"<p>What sets this divan bed apart is the option to add a comfortable mattress of my<br\/>choice. The personalized comfort level is fantastic, and it truly feels like a tailor-made sleep experience. The 28-day return policy provided peace of mind.\"<\/p>","author":"Emma Walker","author_info":"","show_star_rating":true,"star_rating":5}},"testimonial_nXW79p":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"testimonial":"<p>The seamless delivery experience, right to my doorstep, made getting this divan bed a delight! The ground floor delivery option was incredibly convenient. The quality is outstanding, and the 0% interest installment plan made the purchase even more accessible. A top-notch choice for anyone seeking both comfort and convenience!\"<\/p>","author":"Daniel Johnson","author_info":"","show_star_rating":true,"star_rating":5}}},"block_order":["testimonial_twi4ep","testimonial_Pmtnra","testimonial_DkmHBc","testimonial_XVbyqa","testimonial_nXW79p"],"custom_css":[".section__header h2 {color: #fff; font-size: 28px;}"],"settings":{"heading":"Customer Reviews","show_quotes":true,"testimonial_size":"h4","text_position":"justify-center","text_align":"text-center justify-center","nav_style":"slideshow_nav_lines","transition":"slide-fade","autoplay":false,"slider_pause":false,"autoplay_speed":5,"color_scheme":"2","full_width":true}},"recommendations":{"type":"product-recommendations","settings":{"heading":"YOU MAY ALSO LIKE","heading_align":"text-center","layout":"carousel","card_size_mobile":"large","card_size":"medium","products_to_show":8}},"apps_Gy38QG":{"type":"apps","blocks":{"air_product_reviews_app_block_review_list_AxPcjY":{"type":"shopify:\/\/apps\/air-product-reviews\/blocks\/app-block-review-list\/c4e1e9ca-4d46-4e76-bc39-7e42417cb327","settings":{"air_blockreviews_summaryHeading":"Reviews","air_blockreviews_layout":"list","air_blockreviews_singleStarColor":"#16a086","air_blockreviews_primaryColor":"#121212"}}},"block_order":["air_product_reviews_app_block_review_list_AxPcjY"],"settings":{"full_width":false}},"faq_K9VnUr":{"type":"faq","blocks":{"question_kQgbqx":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"What is a divan bed?","text":"<p>A divan bed is a type of bed that typically consists of a mattress on top of a solid base. It is designed for both comfort and functionality, often featuring built-in storage drawers for added convenience.<\/p>"}},"question_3Pe7hU":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"What is the difference between a divan bed and a traditional bed frame?","text":"<p>While both provide mattress support, a divan bed typically features an upholstered base that extends to the floor, creating a seamless and elegant look. It often includes built-in storage options, such as drawers, for added functionality.<\/p>"}},"question_CDYKzb":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"Are divan beds suitable for all mattress sizes?","text":"<p>Yes, our divan beds are available in various sizes, including single, small double, double, king, and super king, accommodating different mattress dimensions for a fit.<\/p>"}},"question_UQXUea":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"Can the divan bed be placed on any flooring type, such as carpet or hardwood?","text":"<p>Yes, our divan beds are versatile and can be placed on various flooring types, including carpet, hardwood, or laminate. The sturdy construction ensures stability on different surfaces.<\/p>"}},"question_ARyiFj":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"Can I return or exchange a divan bed with drawers?","text":"<p>Yes, our standard return policy applies. You have 28 days to return or exchange your divan bed if you are not satisfied. Please review our return policy for more details.<\/p>"}},"question_aPd8UA":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"Are the divan beds available in different colors andstyles?","text":"<p>Yes, we offer a range of colors and styles to suit various preferences and bedroom aesthetics. Explore our catalog to find the perfect divan bed that complements your taste.<\/p>"}},"question_Wqyf8F":{"type":"question","settings":{"icon":"none","heading":"Is there a warranty for the divan bed with drawers?","text":"<p>Yes, all our divan beds come with a 12-month warranty. This warranty covers manufacturing defects and provides assurance of the quality and durability of our products.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["question_kQgbqx","question_3Pe7hU","question_CDYKzb","question_UQXUea","question_ARyiFj","question_aPd8UA","question_Wqyf8F"],"settings":{"heading":"Frequently Asked Questions","heading_align":"text-center","color_scheme":"1","full_width":true}},"logo_list_ECCAjA":{"type":"logo-list","blocks":{"logo_3RKPP7":{"type":"logo","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/dividebuy-logo-full-colour-rgb.png","url":"","logo_width":120,"text":""}},"logo_pjPTWT":{"type":"logo","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Klarna_Payment_Badge_svg.webp","url":"","logo_width":120,"text":""}},"logo_HcXANb":{"type":"logo","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/CP_logo_badge_6328x2204_blackmint_png.png","url":"","logo_width":120,"text":""}},"logo_itQ3RW":{"type":"logo","disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Logo_Grape-black.png","url":"","logo_width":120,"text":""}},"logo_wrtitE":{"type":"logo","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/shop.png","url":"","logo_width":120,"text":""}},"logo_6fK3rA":{"type":"logo","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Google-Pay-logo.png","url":"","logo_width":120,"text":""}},"logo_dJAPxW":{"type":"logo","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/apple-pay-og-twitter.jpg","url":"","logo_width":120,"text":""}},"logo_HUDqe8":{"type":"logo","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/paypal-credit-logo-524CC275C4-seeklogo.com.png","url":"","logo_width":120,"text":""}}},"block_order":["logo_3RKPP7","logo_pjPTWT","logo_HcXANb","logo_itQ3RW","logo_wrtitE","logo_6fK3rA","logo_dJAPxW","logo_HUDqe8"],"settings":{"title":"","heading_align":"text-center","button_label":"","button_link":"","layout":"grid","spacing":40,"logo_grid_align":"justify-center","color_scheme":"none","full_width":true}}},"order":["main","custom_liquid_XJJUaa","details","slideshow_THxMBR","custom_liquid_Fz4yK4","slideshow_Jjfzy7","product_features_FNBXjX","rich_text_Kpk3XR","media_with_text_WrKJx